    {:name "M-typed-holes fill witnesses"
     :path "futon3c/holes/missions/M-typed-holes-*.md"
     :warrant-patterns ["futon-theory/curry-howard-operational"]}
    {:name "state snapshot witnesses"
     :path "futon3c/src/futon3c/logic/snapshot.clj"
     :warrant-patterns ["invariant-coherence/state-snapshot-witness"]}]
   :scan-question
   "For each mission or claim, is there a witness object/proof path, what type does it inhabit, and is that witness durable enough for another agent to check?"}

